            "title": "台股連續兩日回吐 今收跌0.55%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股第2日回吐，台灣加權指數收報39303點，跌218點或0.55%。</p>\n</div>",
